This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which CalPal ("we," "our," or "us") collects, uses, maintains, and discloses information collected from users ("you" or "your") of the CalPal mobile application.

Information Collection and Use:
- Personal Information: CalPal may collect personal information, including but not limited to your name, email address, age, gender, weight, height, and fitness goals, to provide personalized services and optimize your user experience.
