- Device Information: CalPal may gather non-personal information about your device, including the type of device, operating system, unique device identifiers, and other diagnostic data to enhance app performance and user experience.

Data Storage and Security:
- Cloud Storage: Your calorie data is securely encrypted and stored in cloud servers to enable data synchronization between devices. We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.

Information Sharing:
